data.description:
Excellent Location and Low Maintenance Living!  This SouthCreek 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Townhome boasts over 1200 square feet and has everything you need. Upon entering, there is warm sense of being home.  The main family room is inviting, spacious, and a great place to gather.   The Kitchen is open to the family room providing a seamless flow for effortless and enjoyable entertaining.  This cooks kitchen features quartz counters, Stainless appliances, counter space, an eat-in area, pantry, stainless appliances, and great light.  A rear deck is also accessed from the kitchen for grilling and coffee outdoors.  The main level also features a ½ bath and laundry.  Heading to the upper level there is an abundance of natural light coming from all 3 bedrooms.  The primary is large and has a terrific walk-in closet.  The full bath is well situated to serve the bedrooms.  Each secondary bedroom is a great size with plenty of closet storage.  As a bonus - good size Nook allows for the creation of a unique space for storage, toys, or pets. A fully fenced rear yard provides privacy and a natural environment.  This quiet neighborhood is right on the Cherry Creek Trail System, which is steps away with eateries and shopping within walking or biking distance. Schools are in the coveted Cherry Creek District!  Don’t wait – this is a Gem!
